<p>Mark Leviton&rsquo;s interview with Rabbi Michael Lerner [&ldquo;<a href="/article/4702">Loving the Stranger</a>&rdquo;] was fantastic. Lerner&rsquo;s absolutely right that Israel should address its terrorist problems by first ending the occupation of the West Bank and Gaza as a part of a comprehensive peace treaty.</p>
